Tshimenga tshikulu tshia ditunga dia Moldavie ntshia Chişinău. Muakulu wabu wa ku dibele mmuena Roumanie, kadi bantu ba bungi batu bakula tshiena Russie.
Mu ditunga dia Moldavie mudi bantu ba bisamba bia bungi, ne mvita ya bisamba mmivule.
Mu 1994, mvita eyi yakafikisha ku dienza ditunga dia "Transnistria" ku Est kua ditunga dia Moldavie, ditunga didi kadiyi dimanyike kudi ONU, didi ne mbulamatadi ne makuta adi adilombola.
Nansha mudi matunga abidi a mu Moldavie kaayi apetangana mu malu a tshididi, adi ne malu a mpetu mashilangane.
Tshitendelelu tshia mu Moldavie ntshia "bena Kristo ba mu Ortodokse".
Izmir ke tshimenga tshinene tshisatu tshia mu Turquie tshidi ne bantu bapite pa miliyo 3.7, tshidi ne tshitudilu tshinene tshia mazuwa tshibidi panyima pa tshia Istanbul, ne tshidi ne malu mimpe a ngendu.
Tshimenga tshia kale tshia "Smyma" tshidi mpindieu muaba munene wa bungenda-mushinga udi ku muelelu kua mbuu ne mikuna.
Nansha mudi misesu minene ya muinshi mua mabaya, nzubu ya lumuenu ne miaba ya bungenda-mushinga ya matuku etu aa mienza ne tuzubu tua mabaya makunze, bisalu bia mu lukama lua bidimu lua 18 ne nzubu ya nzambi ya kale, tshimenga etshi tshidi ne lungenyi lua bena ku Mputu wa ku Mediterane pamutu pa lua bena mu Turquie wa kale.
Tshimenga tshikese tshia "Haldarsvik" tshidi tshimueneka pabuipi ne tshidiila tshia "Eysturoy", tshidi kabidi ne tshitanda tshia nzambi tshidi ne mpingu ya dikema.
Mu ntempelo amu mudi mpingu ya nyunyi ya nkutshi miteka pa masua.
Nansha tshitupa tshia dîba tshianana tshia kuendakana mu tshimenga etshi tshidi ne mushinga wa bungi.
Ku Nord, muaba wa kumpala uudi ne bua kufika ngua "Sintra", tshimenga tshia disanka tshiakalua kumanyika kudi bena ngendu ba mu matunga makuabu ne kudi bintu bia dikema bia muaba eu bivua "Lord Byron" mufunde.
"Scotturb Bus 403" utu ufika ku "Cabo da Roca" dituku dionso bua kuya ku "Sintra".
Kabidi, ku Nord kudi muaba munene wa tshijila wa "Muaba wa Tshijila wa Mamu wetu wa mu Fatima", muaba udi mpingu ya "Mariya" mimanyike bikole pa buloba bujima.
Tudi tukulomba bua umuambile ne: udi ne bua kuya mu lukita lumue lumue alu ne kumanya kabidi ne: muaba eu ke udibu bajika bantu bapite pa tshia binunu binayi bia pa buloba bujima.
Tudi ne bantu balume ne bakaji ba matuku etu aa bavua bapanduke muaba eu, ne bantu bakuabu, bena Yuda ne bantu ba bisamba bikuabu bavuabu bashipe bananga babu anyi babashipe ku mudimu muaba eu.
Tudi tukulomba bua udienzeje bua kupesha muaba eu lumu, bunême ne kanemu bidi bikumbanyine.
Kabena banyanga muaba eu ne mabue a mupuya muimpe anyi ne bintu bikuabu to.
Bantu ba mu Barcelone batu banange kuakula tshiena Catalogne, ba bungi batu bumvua muakulu eu, ne muakulu wa tshiena Espagne ke udibu bakula bikole
Kadi, bimanyinu bionso bia njila mbifunda mu "Catalan", bualu ke muakulu wa kumpala udibu bakula mu Barcelone.
Nansha nanku, "muakulu wa tshiena-Espagne" mmuakulu udibu benza nawu mudimu bikole mu biamu bia mu tshibuashibuashi ne mu biamu bikuabu.
Muendeshi wa kawulu udi umanyisha malu mu muakulu wa "Catalan", kadi udi umanyisha malu makuabu mu muakulu wa tshiena-Espagne, wa Anglais, wa Mfualansa, wa tshiena-Arabe ne wa tshiena-Japon.
Bantu ba mu "Paris" mbamanyike bua budinangi, dipanga dia kanemu ne lutambishi luabu.
Nansha mudi ngenyi eyi kayiyi milelela, wewe musue kushala mu tshimenga tshia Paris, udi ne bua kuikala ne bikadilu bimpe eku udimona bu udi mukolele bimpe.
Bantu ba mu "Paris" batu bamueneka diakamue padibu babambuluisha mu tumalu tukese.
Mu lupangu lua dijiba dia "Plitvice" mudi mitshi ya "beech", "spruce", ne "fir" ne mitshi ya "Alpine" ne ya "Mediterranean".
Mu bikondo bia mashika makole, miaba mishilashilangane ne mikuna mishilashilangane, mitshi itu isampila miaba mishilashilangane.
Muaba eu udi kabidi muaba udi nyama ne nyunyi ya mishindu ne mishindu.
