Bua kubuela mu nzubu wa badiambike, bantu bakaji badi ne bua kudienzeja bua kuvuala muzabi mukese udi ubuikila too ne ku binu ne ku dikaya.
Kudi bilamba bitubu bapesha bantu bakaji badi kabayi badilengeje kumpala kua kubuela mu kuvan, kadi wewe mulue ne tshilamba tshia panshi tshidi ne mekala a bungi a butoke bua mupuya muimpe, nsongalume anyi nsongakaji udi ukuenzela mudimu udi mua kukuenzelatshi ku tshiibi.
Bana-balume badi ne bua kulonda mukenji wa muomumue pa kuvuala mizabi bua kubuikila binu.
Imue ya ku mizabi eyi ivua mua kuikala mikusombeshe ku tshiibi, kadi kuvua mua kuikala mumvue bimpe bua kuvuala muzabi wetu wa pa mutu to.
Mulamba wa "Majorcan" udi mufuanangane ne wa miaba mikuabu ya ku Mediterane, udi ne mampa, bisekiseki ne munyinyi (nangananga nyama wa ngulube) ne mafuta a olive.
Mu tshikondo tshia luya, bavua badia "Pa amb Oli": mampa ne mafuta a olive, bisekiseki, ne bintu bikuabu bu mudi: mabele, bisekiseki, ne bikuabu.
Miaku ya mu kasumbu ka miaku ne "Wewe" yonso mmifunda ne maleta manene, nansha yoyi munkatshi mua tshiambilu.
Eu mmushindu muimpe wa kuleja dishilangana didi pankatshi pa miaku ya pa muanda ne bienzedi.
Nansha mudi miaku eyi mikale mikole bua kubala padi muaku wa pa muanda anyi wa muaku wa pa muanda muikale muaku wa pa muanda, idi yambuluisha bua kubala bipepele.
Muakulu wa tshiena Italie udi ne ngakuilu mupepele bualu badi bafunda miaku ne bayitela mushindu umue
Muaku "c" ne "g" ke udi ne mushinga wa bungi, bualu miaku idi ku ndekelu kua maleta abidi aa idi mua kushintulula mushindu wa kuakula.
Kabidi, ikala mumanye mua kutapulula mushindu uudi utela "r" ne "rr": "caro" udi umvuija munanga, ne "carro" udi umvuija ditempu.
Muakulu wa tshiena Perse udi ne ngakuilu mupepele udi ne mikenji ya nshindamenu mijalame.
Ke bualu kayi dilonga dia mukanda eu didi mua kukuambuluisha bua kumanya mikenji ya muakulu wa bena Pelasa ne kumvua bimpe biambilu biabu.
Bushuwa, kumanya muakulu kampanda wa bena Lomo kudi mua kukuambuluisha bua kulonga Tshimputulukeshi kakuyi lutatu.
Kadi bantu badi bakula tshiena-Espagne badi bamba ne lukasa ne: Tshimputulukeshi tshidi pabuipi menemene ne tshiena-Espagne, nunku kabiena ne mushinga bua kulonga Tshimputulukeshi to.
Miaba ya kale ivuabu batangila bikata bia mitoto ne mabulunge mmishale anu miaba ya kulamina bintu bia kale anyi ya kulongela malu.
Nansha muvuabi kabiyi bimanyine pa makunji bu mudibi lelu, bantu bavua batemesha miendu mu bimenga binene anyi mu tulasa, kakuyi lutatu lua bungi to.
Makamera a matuku etu aa mmatangalake bikole mu miaba ya kule idi bantu batamba kuimanyina pa malu a mu diulu.
Katshia mu bidimu bia 700, Hanami mmulue bumue bua ku bilele bia bena Japon.
Tshilele etshi tshiakamueneka mu ditunga dia Chine pavua bimuma bia mupuya muimpe biende lumu bikole.
Mu ditunga dia Japon, mamuende wa mfumu ne wa banene ba mu Tshilumbuluidi tshia Ampire ke uvua ne tumuma tupite bunene.
Mitshi ya mfigi itu yenda bimpe mu miaba idi mitshi mipuekele, nunku kuikadi uditatshisha bua kushipa nansha umue wa ku mitshi eyi to, nansha "umue".
Paudi ubuela mu budimi bua mitshi budibu balongolole bimpe, badi mua kukuipata wewe mutuadije "kulonda njila yonso" kuyi muanji kuyukila ne muntu.
Singapour mmuaba muimpe wa kuenzela ngendu ne kupitshisha kapepe.
Kadi padibu bakuteka ku "nzubu wa tshilala benyi" wa ku Nord muaba udi dîba dipite bungi, udi ne bua kuvuluka ne: udi ne bua kuluangana ne luya (luikala lutungunuka dituku dionso) ne tshilamba tshia kuikishila ku munya (tshidibu kabayi batamba kukuata mu bikondo bia mashika).
Mikuna mikuabu idi ku nord kua Hebelone, muaba udibu bajika bantu badibu batele mu Mifundu minsantu bu mudi: Abalahama, Izaka, Yakoba ne bakaji babu.
Ikala mushindike ne: mashinyi audi ukeba bua kuya nawu adi anu bua kuya ku Hebelone ne kaakufikisha pabuipi ne musoko wa bena Yuda wa Kiriata-Araba to.
Misulu ya ku muelelu kua mâyi itu kabidi miaba mimpe ya kuikishila.
Tshilejilu, udi mua kuya kumona nzubu minene ya mu Tshibandabanda tshia Loire, tshia Rhine, anyi kuya mu bimenga bia ku muelelu kua musulu wa Danube anyi kuya kuendakana mu Canal d'Érié.
Badi kabidi mua kuleja njila idi bantu bapitshila ne idibu bendesha pa tubalu tua biamu.
Nowele ndituku dinene dia bena Kristo bua kusekelela diledibua dia Yezu.
Malu adibu benza mu tshibilu etshi mmalu adi bantu ba mu matunga a bena Kristo ne ba mu matunga adi kaayi a bena Kristo benza pa buloba bujima.
Dilolo dia mufikilu wa lufu lua Yezu, bantu batu benza tshilele tshia kuimana mu bule bua butuku bua kumona dîba dipatuka mu dinda.
Badi ne diumvuija kampanda dia malu a Nzambi bua tshilele etshi, kadi tshidi mua kuikala tshilele tshia Dimueneka ne Dibuela mu Buena-Kristo.
Mu bitanda bia bungi batu benza Tshivulukilu tshia lufu lua Yezu mu Disambombo dilolo, ne munkatshi mua butuku bantu batu bela mbila bua kuleja disanka diabu bua dibika dia Yezu ku lufu.
Nyama yonso ya mu tshidiila etshi ivua ilua muaba eu bua kuowa mâyi, kuendakana, anyi bua kunua.
Bu muvua luendu lule, nyama eyi kayivua mua kumbuka mu tshidiila to, ke bualu kayi tshimpanga tshinene etshi tshiakalua nyama wa mu tshidiila tshia Galapagos.
Bantu mbalue ne nyama bu mudi mbuji, tubalu, ngombe, mpasu ne mbua mu bidiila bia Galapagos.
Wewe muye mu tshitupa tshia buloba tshidi ne mashika makole anyi mu tshitupa tshia buloba tshidi ne mashika makole mu tshikondo tshia mashika makole, neutete butuku bua mêba mapite pa makumi abidi ne anayi, mbuena kuamba ne: dîba kadiena dianji kupitshila mu tshikoso tshia buloba to.
Bualu ebu budi bukupetesha mushindu wa kumona "Aurora Borealis" dîba dionso didi butoke bukese.
Bu mudi miaba eyi kayiyi ne bantu ba bungi ne kayiyi ne nzembu ya bungi, diulu didi ne mitoto nedikusankishe.
Dienza mudimu mu Japon didi ne bulongame ne ndishilangane bikole ne dia ku Mputu.
Tshilamba tshia pa mutu ntshilamba tshia mudimu tshidibu banyisha ne bena mudimu batu badibikila ku mêna abu anyi ku midimu yabu.
Bidi bikengela kuikala mu buobumue ne kuenza mudimu bimpe pamue pamutu pa kuimanyina anu pa bipeta bimpe bia muntu pa nkayende.
Bena mudimu badi ne bua kuenza muabu muonso bua kuangata mapangadika ne kutumikila bamfumu babu kakuyi dielakana.
